1) createtransaction -> create a transaction object with given details
2) convert transaction object into a file
		OR
1&2) make transaction as a file

3) use gnunet to publish transaction
4) receive transaction file using gnunet
5) convert transaction text into an object
6) validate the transaction object and add to the block of transactions

1) create a transacton block (include special coin creation transaction ) and fill in with transaction objects
2) solve the proof of work
3) propose a transaction block
4) rcvng node check if the nonce is correct
5) receive a proposed transaction block and decide whether to add it to the consensus chain
	
1) create a wallet ( pvt key, pub key)
2) find your balance:
	start from the block chain head
	move upwards till u find a transaction giving u coin or a transaction created by u
		if it's a transaction created by u
			that'll contain ur balance
		else 
			add the coins given to u by that transaction 	
